<item>
            <title>[LU-20022] zfs txg not advancing on mdt</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-20022</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We recently saw what looks like a deadlock on the MDTs of our yuba cluster. When checking /proc/spl/kstat/zfs/&amp;lt;pool_name&amp;gt;/txgs, the txg number was not advancing for tens of minutes and the affected nodes had to be rebooted. This happened on several of the MDT nodes all around the same time.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>lustre-2.15.7_3.llnl-1.3shs13.t4.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
zfs-2.2.8_6llnl-1.t4.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
toss 4.8-21&lt;br/&gt;
kernel 4.18.0-553.104.1.1toss.t4.x86_64</environment>
