&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ptlrpc_main+0xc32/0x1590 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;ptlrpc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; kthread+0x14c/0x170&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; ret_from_fork+0x35/0x40&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Threads like this blocked in `dmu_tx_wait` are waiting on the above thread to commit its TX.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Call Trace TBD:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&amp;lt;0&amp;gt;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; cv_wait_common+0x106/0x130 &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;spl&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
